#### Q14. Java – Short-Circuit Evaluation

Consider the following Java code:

```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int x = 0;
        if (x != 0 && 10 / x > 1) {
            System.out.println("A");
        } else {
            System.out.println("B");
        }
    }
}
```

What is the output?

A. A  
B. B  
C. Runtime error (ArithmeticException)  
D. Compilation error  

**Correct answer: B**
